{"tid":1473901,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳雲：中美有機會借助香港，進入和平議程","createTime":"2019-08-15T03:40:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T04:37:24.000Z","uid":111150,"like":16,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"9546e2a75c57b312e2d794f39388c6701dfc608c","tid":1473901,"uid":111150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T03:40:23.000Z","msg":"陳雲：中美有機會借助香港，進入和平議程，而且以香港民主做優先的合作試驗基地。這段空檔，至為危險！各位務必參考我的說話，暫停所有衝擊性質的社運，等候中美雙方和談。改為整理資料，製作文宣及短片宣傳，持續影響美國議員及民意，催谷《香港人權及民主法案》通過。<br />\n我們要民主，但也有人是不要的！香港民主是損害好多既得利益者的，目前在香港犯錯的官員在民主化之後也恐懼受到懲罰，故此一旦有衝擊性質的社運，必會有人騎劫或破壞，製造傷亡事件，故此各位前線的兄弟姐妹，請務必堅忍，暫停衝擊性質的社運。請將社運定格在星期日的完美受害人位置，不要輕舉妄動。<br />\n陳雲在此，正義必會降臨香港。"},{"pid":"b97ee0a3719690dcd5355c8b7ca1ce806db49d7f","tid":1473901,"uid":274136,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T03:50:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><em><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">不撤不散 各自努力<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n長期戰 不氣餒</span></ins></em></strong></span><br />\n唔好意思，阻你一陣<br />\n-<br />\n香港人重要日程：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>8月15日</strong>：稅局接收工（1200稅務大樓）</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>8月16日</strong>：學界萬人炒聯手萬人集會（2000遮打花園）<br />\n<strong>8月16日</strong>：大家記得撳錢</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><strong>8月17日</strong>：教師大遊行（1100遮打花園）<br />\n<strong>8月17日</strong>：光復紅土（1530紅磡馬頭）</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>8月18日</strong>：民陣大遊行（1500維園）</span></ins></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><strong>8月24日</strong>：觀塘大遊行（1300駿業街球場）</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><strong>8月25日</strong>：荃葵青遊街（1400葵青劇院集合）</span><br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">各位手足，到時見！</span></strong>"},{"pid":"25b23a6760c4e1cb0a08c0b87cac78973e85b424","tid":1473901,"uid":111150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T03:50:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"86c8cc515ebb8894ca60e8270c63f6914d5e88ff","tid":1473901,"uid":95520,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T03:53:20.000Z","msg":"連N年前就主張勇武嘅國師都咁講"},{"pid":"3e7c7d1dbcd970a9d932fb08d3434b3290204e2d","tid":1473901,"uid":99962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T03:55:50.000Z","msg":"希望連登仔討論呢篇文唔好再討論佢既病"},{"pid":"26bb6101de9b2b5f34b1809b3d9f5f737ec3d472","tid":1473901,"uid":111150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T03:58:21.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"edb53486c6acded678d1b2b24fd77c10feb0aa79","tid":1473901,"uid":75782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T04:02:55.000Z","msg":"與沈旭暉一致論調"},{"pid":"f3c68483bff6ed0a889a2df5fcc495530bec8357","tid":1473901,"uid":132030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T04:05:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f0c5e6e4f52fb9c895a350295466da2e07640ef7","tid":1473901,"uid":283157,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T04:05:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ef6f7af10e98a93fc7de1bdb854fb51816e7b18b","tid":1473901,"uid":171866,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T04:15:19.000Z","msg":"呢次撑佢同我諗既一樣<br />\n一定係去盡無所不用其極"},{"pid":"98af05d6c1b1ab78731df5fcae9c181fdde56d59","tid":1473901,"uid":187538,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T04:20:41.000Z","msg":"大家可以輕鬆下先<br />\n818 大家行完就走<br />\n之後仲有眾籌左嘅G20 x 攬炒團隊全世界登報<br />\n可以慢慢做下文宣先<br />\n比外國少少時間去反應發聲<br />\n推動香港人權法"},{"pid":"0041997fbb06fe993c81261ce8aa366a8fc3bdd0","tid":1473901,"uid":33437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T04:28:41.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"1373a6124ee7870a9728caa18ded20f923b492b7","tid":1473901,"uid":52596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T04:29:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/a